column3: I have updated the remote jar repositories to contain the repository for org.jetbrains:markdown:0.1.31
Otherwise, the build fails if the library is not yet in the local maven repository with this error:
14:45	Repository library synchronization: No files were downloaded for org.jetbrains:markdown:0.1.31
Merged to 'master', thank you for the fix!
jarRepositories.xml: Missing maven repo for JetBrain's markdown library
